State of North Carolina
v.
Richard Lee Nealen No. 258P16 Supreme Court of North Carolina. July 12, 2016. Richard Lee Nealen, for Nealen, Richard Lee. Robert C. Montgomery, Special Deputy Attorney General, for State of N.C.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the application filed by Petitioner on the 11th of July 2016 in this matter for Writ of Habeas Corpus, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the Superior Court, Catawba County:

"Denied by order of the Court in conference, this the 11th of July 2016."
